Class SuperTestSuite

java.lang.Object
SuperTestSuite
@Suite
@SelectClasses({ModelTestSuite.class,OrderTestSuite.class,StartupPhaseTest.class,InvalidMapTest.class,UtilsTestSuite.class,DemoDriverTestSuite.class})
public class SuperTestSuite
extends java.lang.Object
The SuperTestSuite class is the top-level JUnit 5 test suite for the entire project. It includes various sub-test suites covering different aspects of the project's functionality. Sub-suites included in this SuperTestSuite:
  • ModelTestSuite: Tests for the Models package, covering data structures and game components.
  • OrderTestSuite: Tests for order-related functionality.
  • StartupPhaseTest: Tests for the game startup phase and initialization.
  • InvalidMapTest: Tests for invalid map configurations.
  • UtilsTestSuite: Tests for utility classes and helpers.
  • DemoDriverTestSuite: Tests for the demo driver or user interface components.
Usage: To execute all the tests for the entire project, run this class as a JUnit test.
